        "headline": "USN-8068-1: Intel Microcode vulnerability",
        "content": {
          "excerpt_text": "Sergiu Ghetie discovered that some Intel® processors did not properly handle values in the microcode flow. A local authenticated user could potentially use this issue to escalate their privileges.",
          "lang": "en"
        },
        "provenance": {
