        "updated_at": "2026-03-02T17:29:15Z",
        "headline": "USN-8067-1: Mailman vulnerability",
        "content": {
          "excerpt_text": "It was discovered that Mailman incorrectly handled CSRF tokens. A remote list member or moderator could possibly use their own token to craft an admin request CSRF attack and set a new admin password or make other changes.",
          "lang": "en"
        },
        "provenance": {
